{
  "chapter": {
    "id": "web:first-chronicles.8",
    "translationId": "web",
    "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
    "chapterNumber": 8,
    "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 8",
    "summary": "Source text for 1 Chronicles 8 in World English Bible."
  },
  "verses": [
    {
      "id": "web:first-chronicles.8.1",
      "translationId": "web",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 8,
      "verseNumber": 1,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 8:1",
      "text": "Benjamin became the father of Bela his firstborn, Ashbel the second, Aharah the third,",
      "paragraphStart": true
    },
    {
      "id": "web:first-chronicles.8.2",
      "translationId": "web",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 8,
      "verseNumber": 2,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 8:2",
      "text": "Nohah the fourth, and Rapha the fifth.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "web:first-chronicles.8.3",
      "translationId": "web",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 8,
      "verseNumber": 3,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 8:3",
      "text": "Bela had sons: Addar, Gera, Abihud,",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "web:first-chronicles.8.4",
      "translationId": "web",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 8,
      "verseNumber": 4,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 8:4",
      "text": "Abishua, Naaman, Ahoah,",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "web:first-chronicles.8.5",
      "translationId": "web",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 8,
      "verseNumber": 5,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 8:5",
      "text": "Gera, Shephuphan, and Huram.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "web:first-chronicles.8.6",
      "translationId": "web",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 8,
      "verseNumber": 6,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 8:6",
      "text": "These are the sons of Ehud. These are the heads of fathers’ households of the inhabitants of Geba, who were carried captive to Manahath:",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "web:first-chronicles.8.7",
      "translationId": "web",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 8,
      "verseNumber": 7,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 8:7",
      "text": "Naaman, Ahijah, and Gera, who carried them captive; and he became the father of Uzza and Ahihud.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "web:first-chronicles.8.8",
      "translationId": "web",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 8,
      "verseNumber": 8,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 8:8",
      "text": "Shaharaim became the father of children in the field of Moab, after he had sent them away. Hushim and Baara were his wives.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "web:first-chronicles.8.9",
      "translationId": "web",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 8,
      "verseNumber": 9,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 8:9",
      "text": "By Hodesh his wife, he became the father of Jobab, Zibia, Mesha, Malcam,",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "web:first-chronicles.8.10",
      "translationId": "web",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 8,
      "verseNumber": 10,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 8:10",
      "text": "Jeuz, Shachia, and Mirmah. These were his sons, heads of fathers’ households.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "web:first-chronicles.8.11",
      "translationId": "web",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 8,
      "verseNumber": 11,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 8:11",
      "text": "By Hushim, he became the father of Abitub and Elpaal.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "web:first-chronicles.8.12",
      "translationId": "web",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 8,
      "verseNumber": 12,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 8:12",
      "text": "The sons of Elpaal: Eber, Misham, and Shemed, who built Ono and Lod, with its towns;",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "web:first-chronicles.8.13",
      "translationId": "web",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 8,
      "verseNumber": 13,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 8:13",
      "text": "and Beriah and Shema, who were heads of fathers’ households of the inhabitants of Aijalon, who put to flight the inhabitants of Gath;",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "web:first-chronicles.8.14",
      "translationId": "web",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 8,
      "verseNumber": 14,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 8:14",
      "text": "and Ahio, Shashak, Jeremoth,",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "web:first-chronicles.8.15",
      "translationId": "web",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 8,
      "verseNumber": 15,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 8:15",
      "text": "Zebadiah, Arad, Eder,",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "web:first-chronicles.8.16",
      "translationId": "web",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 8,
      "verseNumber": 16,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 8:16",
      "text": "Michael, Ishpah, Joha, the sons of Beriah,",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "web:first-chronicles.8.17",
      "translationId": "web",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 8,
      "verseNumber": 17,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 8:17",
      "text": "Zebadiah, Meshullam, Hizki, Heber,",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "web:first-chronicles.8.18",
      "translationId": "web",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 8,
      "verseNumber": 18,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 8:18",
      "text": "Ishmerai, Izliah, Jobab, the sons of Elpaal,",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "web:first-chronicles.8.19",
      "translationId": "web",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 8,
      "verseNumber": 19,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 8:19",
      "text": "Jakim, Zichri, Zabdi,",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "web:first-chronicles.8.20",
      "translationId": "web",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 8,
      "verseNumber": 20,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 8:20",
      "text": "Elienai, Zillethai, Eliel,",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "web:first-chronicles.8.21",
      "translationId": "web",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 8,
      "verseNumber": 21,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 8:21",
      "text": "Adaiah, Beraiah, Shimrath, the sons of Shimei,",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "web:first-chronicles.8.22",
      "translationId": "web",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 8,
      "verseNumber": 22,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 8:22",
      "text": "Ishpan, Eber, Eliel,",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "web:first-chronicles.8.23",
      "translationId": "web",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 8,
      "verseNumber": 23,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 8:23",
      "text": "Abdon, Zichri, Hanan,",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "web:first-chronicles.8.24",
      "translationId": "web",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 8,
      "verseNumber": 24,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 8:24",
      "text": "Hananiah, Elam, Anthothijah,",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "web:first-chronicles.8.25",
      "translationId": "web",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 8,
      "verseNumber": 25,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 8:25",
      "text": "Iphdeiah, Penuel, the sons of Shashak,",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "web:first-chronicles.8.26",
      "translationId": "web",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 8,
      "verseNumber": 26,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 8:26",
      "text": "Shamsherai, Shehariah, Athaliah,",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "web:first-chronicles.8.27",
      "translationId": "web",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 8,
      "verseNumber": 27,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 8:27",
      "text": "Jaareshiah, Elijah, Zichri, and the sons of Jeroham.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "web:first-chronicles.8.28",
      "translationId": "web",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 8,
      "verseNumber": 28,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 8:28",
      "text": "These were heads of fathers’ households throughout their generations, chief men. These lived in Jerusalem.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "web:first-chronicles.8.29",
      "translationId": "web",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 8,
      "verseNumber": 29,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 8:29",
      "text": "The father of Gibeon, whose wife’s name was Maacah, lived in Gibeon",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "web:first-chronicles.8.30",
      "translationId": "web",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 8,
      "verseNumber": 30,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 8:30",
      "text": "with his firstborn son Abdon, Zur, Kish, Baal, Nadab,",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "web:first-chronicles.8.31",
      "translationId": "web",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 8,
      "verseNumber": 31,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 8:31",
      "text": "Gedor, Ahio, Zecher,",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "web:first-chronicles.8.32",
      "translationId": "web",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 8,
      "verseNumber": 32,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 8:32",
      "text": "and Mikloth, who became the father of Shimeah. They also lived with their families in Jerusalem, near their relatives.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "web:first-chronicles.8.33",
      "translationId": "web",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 8,
      "verseNumber": 33,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 8:33",
      "text": "Ner became the father of Kish. Kish became the father of Saul. Saul became the father of Jonathan, Malchishua, Abinadab, and Eshbaal.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "web:first-chronicles.8.34",
      "translationId": "web",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 8,
      "verseNumber": 34,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 8:34",
      "text": "The son of Jonathan was Merib-baal. Merib-baal became the father of Micah.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "web:first-chronicles.8.35",
      "translationId": "web",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 8,
      "verseNumber": 35,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 8:35",
      "text": "The sons of Micah: Pithon, Melech, Tarea, and Ahaz.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "web:first-chronicles.8.36",
      "translationId": "web",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 8,
      "verseNumber": 36,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 8:36",
      "text": "Ahaz became the father of Jehoaddah. Jehoaddah became the father of Alemeth, Azmaveth, and Zimri. Zimri became the father of Moza.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "web:first-chronicles.8.37",
      "translationId": "web",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 8,
      "verseNumber": 37,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 8:37",
      "text": "Moza became the father of Binea. Raphah was his son, Eleasah his son, and Azel his son.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "web:first-chronicles.8.38",
      "translationId": "web",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 8,
      "verseNumber": 38,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 8:38",
      "text": "Azel had six sons, whose names are these: Azrikam, Bocheru, Ishmael, Sheariah, Obadiah, and Hanan. All these were the sons of Azel.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "web:first-chronicles.8.39",
      "translationId": "web",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 8,
      "verseNumber": 39,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 8:39",
      "text": "The sons of Eshek his brother: Ulam his firstborn, Jeush the second, and Eliphelet the third.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "web:first-chronicles.8.40",
      "translationId": "web",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 8,
      "verseNumber": 40,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 8:40",
      "text": "The sons of Ulam were mighty men of valor, archers, and had many sons, and grandsons, one hundred fifty. All these were of the sons of Benjamin.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    }
  ]
}
